script.name: !patch
script.sourceplaintext:
if $a.ver == 3 $game.start = get game start id if $game.start == 1000 $hq = get station array: of race Player class/type=Headquarters if $hq = [PLAYERSHIP] -> add 1 units of Low Frequency Locator = [PLAYERSHIP] -> add 1 units of Interplanetary Drive System end end
$ships = find all ships with job ID=412 if $ships $s = get next key: table=$ships key=null while $s @ START $s -> call script !job.trade.blackmarket : $s = get next key: table=$ships key=$s end end $ships = find all ships with job ID=413 if $ships $s = get next key: table=$ships key=null while $s @ START $s -> call script !job.trade.blackmarket : $s = get next key: table=$ships key=$s end end else if $a.ver == 5 set notoriety of NMMC -> Duke's to [Notoriety.Neutral] points set notoriety of Duke's -> NMMC to [Notoriety.Neutral] points set notoriety of NMMC -> Yaki to [Notoriety.Enemy] points set notoriety of Yaki -> NMMC to [Notoriety.Enemy] points
$ware = Relay Beacon add blueprints to player HQ: type=$ware
* find any stuck TOA $pids = get all global tasks with script: plugin.expguild.npcclaim if $pids $i = size of array $pids while $i dec $i = $pid = $pids[$i] kill global script: pid=$pid end end
$x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y skip if $sector -> exists continue $owner = $sector -> get owner race skip if $owner continue
if $sector ->is sector proposed $flags = [Find.Hyperspeed] | [Find.ExcludeGates] | [Find.ExcludeTerranGates] $hsap = find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$sector, max dist=null, refpos=null if $hsap -> exists $hsap.owner = $hsap -> get owner race if $hsap.owner != Neutral Race AND $hsap.owner != Player $ships = get ship array: of race $hsap.owner class/type=TL if $ships $i = size of array $ships while $i dec $i = $s = $ships[$i] if $s -> get amount of ware Trans-Orbital Accelerator Construction Kit in cargo bay = $s -> add -1 units of Trans-Orbital Accelerator Construction Kit $s ->set boarding allowed: [TRUE] $s ->set race logic control enabled to [TRUE] @ START $s -> call script !lib.interrupt : $s ->start job end end end
$dest.hsap = $hsap -> get gate destination: return sector=[FALSE] @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.expguild.npc.buildtoa : HSAP=$dest.hsap end end end end end
$aStations = get station array: of race Teladi class/type=Teladi Space Equipment Dock $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $st ->add product to factory or dock: Build Command Software MK1 $st ->add product to factory or dock: Build Command Software MK2 end $aStations = get station array: of race Pirates class/type=Pirate Anarchy Port $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $st ->add product to factory or dock: Build Command Software MK1 $st ->add product to factory or dock: Build Command Software MK2 end $aStations = get station array: of race Pirates class/type=Pirate Base $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $st ->add product to factory or dock: Build Command Software MK1 end $aStations = get station array: of race Terran class/type=USC Orbital Support Station $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $st ->add product to factory or dock: Build Command Software MK1 end $aStations = get station array: of race Terran class/type=USC Orbital Logistics Dock $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $st ->add product to factory or dock: Build Command Software MK2 end
$type = Terran Fusion Beam Cannon Forge $aStations = get station array: of race Strong Arms class/type=Strong Arms Strong Arms Shipyard $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $st ->remove product from factory or dock: $type end
$aStations = get station array: of race Terran class/type=Shipyard $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $type = Terran Fusion Beam Cannon Forge if $st -> trades with ware $type $st ->remove product from factory or dock: $type $type = Terran Fusion Beam Cannon Forge $st ->add product to factory or dock: $type end $type = Terran Orbital Laser Factory M if $st -> trades with ware $type $st ->remove product from factory or dock: $type $type = Terran Orbital Laser Factory M $st ->add product to factory or dock: $type end end
$type = NMMC Nividium Mine L $aStations = get station array: of race NMMC class/type=Shipyard $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $st = $aStations[$i] $st ->remove product from factory or dock: $type end
$races = get race array $i = size of array $races while $i dec $i = $race = $races[$i] $ships = get ship array: of race $race class/type=Stationary Ship if $ships $j = size of array $ships while $j dec $j = $s = $ships[$j] if $s -> is script !job.special.idle on stack of task=0 @ START $s -> call script !job.special.idle : end end @ = wait 100 ms $j = size of array $ships while $j dec $j = $s = $ships[$j] if not $s -> is task 0 in use @ START $s -> call script !job.special.idle : end end end
$ships = get ship array: of race $race class/type=Moveable Ship if $ships $j = size of array $ships while $j dec $j = $s = $ships[$j] if $s -> is of class M1 if not $s -> get max speed = $s -> add -100 units of Jump Beacon = $s -> add 1 units of Cargo Bay Shielding end end if $s -> is script !move.resupply.self on stack of task=0 $sector = $s -> get sector $job = $s -> get job id if $job $s ->start task 0 with script !lib.interrupt and prio 100: arg1=null arg2=null arg3=null arg4=null arg5=null $s ->start job end end end end end
* ======================= else if $a.ver == 7 $the.moon = get sector from universe index: x=16, y=2 if $the.moon -> exists $sy = find station: sector=$the.moon class or type=Shipyard race=Terran flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null if $sy -> exists $ware = Terran Fusion Beam Cannon Forge $sy ->add product to factory or dock: $ware end end
$ships = get ship array: of race Player class/type=Kogarasu Maru if $ships $i = size of array $ships while $i dec $i = $ship = $ships[$i] $max.marines = $ship ->get max marines from lookup table $ship ->set current max marines: $max.marines, remove marines=[FALSE] end end
$sy = find station: sector=$the.moon class or type=Pirate Anarchy Port race=Pirates flags=[Find.Multiple] refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=10 refpos=null $kingdom.end = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=1 if $kingdom.end -> exists $docks = find station in galaxy: startsector=$kingdom.end class or type=Pirate Anarchy Port race=Pirates flags=[Find.Multiple] refobj=null serial=null max.jumps=100 if is datatype[ $docks ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $i = size of array $docks while $i dec $i = $s = $docks[$i] $s ->add product to factory or dock: Jumpdrive end else if $docks -> exists $docks ->add product to factory or dock: Jumpdrive end end
$races = get race array $i = size of array $races while $i dec $i = $race = $races[$i] $ships = get ship array: of race $race class/type=Carrier if $ships $j = size of array $ships while $j dec $j = $s = $ships[$j] $job = $s -> get job id if $job if $s -> is script !fight.attack.object.carrier on stack of task=0 $s ->start task 0 with script !lib.interrupt and prio 100: arg1=null arg2=null arg3=null arg4=null arg5=null $s ->start job end end end end end else if $a.ver == 8 $ships = find all ships with job ID=417 if $ships $i = size of array $ships while $i dec $i = $ship = $ships[$i] @ START $ship -> call script !job.collect.marines : end end $jobs = create new array, arguments=414, 415, 416, null, null $job = size of array $jobs while $job dec $job = $job.id = $jobs[$job] $ships = find all ships with job ID=$job.id if $ships $i = size of array $ships while $i dec $i = $ship = $ships[$i] @ START $ship -> call script !job.scavenge : end end end else if $a.ver == 10 = [PLAYERSHIP] -> add 1 units of Unfocussed Jumpdrive
else if $a.ver == 12 $aStations = get station array: of race Pirates class/type=Shipyard if $aStations $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $s = $aStations[$i] $ware = Pirate Base $s ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Anarchy Port $s ->add product to factory or dock: $ware end end $aStations = find all stations with product: ware=Energy Cells, class=Factory, flags=null, refobj=null if $aStations $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $s = $aStations[$i] $owner = $s -> get owner race if $owner != Player if $s -> uses ware Energy Cells as primary resource if $s -> uses ware Energy Cells as secondary resource $s ->remove second resource from factory: Energy Cells end end end end end
else if $a.ver == 15 $sector = get sector from universe index: x=2, y=15 if $sector -> exists $sector.owner = $sector -> get owner race if $sector.owner == Split $aStations = $sector -> get station array from sector if $aStations $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $s = $aStations[$i] $s.owner = $s -> get owner race if $s.owner == Argon $s ->set owner race to Split end end end end end else if $a.ver == 16 * Argon Prime $sector = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=4 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=4 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=2, y=4 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=2, y=3 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=0 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=0 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=1 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=1 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=4, y=1 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=4, y=2 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=5, y=1 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=5, y=2 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=6, y=2 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=7, y=2 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=8, y=2 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=7, y=1 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=7, y=3 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=9 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=9 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=2, y=9 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=8 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=10 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=16, y=3 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE]
else if $a.ver == 17 $sector = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=2 if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [FALSE] $sector ->set sector to core security [FALSE] end $sector = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=4 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=1, y=4 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=2, y=4 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE]
$sector = get sector from universe index: x=16, y=3 do if $sector -> exists $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE]
* fix invincible stations $x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y if $sector -> exists $aStations = $sector -> get station array from sector if $aStations $i = size of array $aStations while $i dec $i = $s = $aStations[$i] if not $s -> is of class Headquarters if not $s -> is of type Xenon Hub $s ->set invincible: enabled=[FALSE] end end end end end end end
else if $a.ver == 18 $plot.flags = get plot flags if $plot.flags & [PlotFlg.Terran] $start.id = get game start id if $start.id == 1000 send script event: name='terran.link', object=[PLAYERSHIP], param1=null, param2=null end end
else if $a.ver == 19 $aRaces = get race array: include fixed=[FALSE], include corporations=[TRUE], include player=[FALSE] $i = size of array $aRaces while $i dec $i = $race.1 = $aRaces[$i]
$j = size of array $aRaces while $j dec $j = $race.2 = $aRaces[$j]
if $race.1 != $race.2 $noto = get notoriety from race $race.1 to race $race.2 do if $noto == -100 set notoriety of $race.1 -> $race.2 to -1000 points end end
end end
return null
